ht|o|at|How can you distinguish Jordan 2NT and not get it confused with Jacoby 2NT, even though both conventions use the same 2NT bid and both conventions start with a J? You keep in mind that Jordan, with a D, is only used after the opponents' takeout ^*BD^*Nouble (with a D). |
